In an emergency conference, we have decided to become an interconfesionl Christian Party that encompasses all of the regular people of Germany, not just Catholics. The Left and Center claim that our new party platform is a betrayal of our founding principles, a turn away from Political Catholicism. Whatever the case, we are now a party representing all of the people, not just Catholics.

